parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key can be removed from the ignition while the engine is still running
the key gets stuck in the ignition
the vehicle stalls or fails to start
and the vehicle may shut down while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or fails to start
the horn comes on when the car is off
and the low tire pressure light stays on even when the tires are fine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall or catch fire, which can lead to accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine compartment fires can cause significant damage to the vehicle, and in some cases, lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle's engine compartment catches fire
often with no warning signs or symptoms beforehand. The fire may be accompanied by smoke

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Oil leaks can cause engine failure, leading to costly repairs or even engine replacement. In some cases, oil leaks can also cause engine compartment fires.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Intake manifold failure can cause engine failure, leading to costly repairs or even engine replacement. In some cases, intake manifold failure can also cause engine compartment fires.

The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to become loose or difficult to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
